    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit maintains its mechanical integrity with a linear power delivery peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to the M Variable Differential Lock and EDC-equipped suspension, ensuring optimal lateral grip and damping control. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated throttle actuators and a comprehensive fluid analysis to monitor rod bearing health. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the atmospheric induction and hydraulic steering rack provide a raw, communicative feedback loop often missing in modern counterparts. A mechanically sound example for the purist looking for an unadulterated S65 experience.",
